file.name: debug-body.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: 'mixed content types'
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /bar:
    post:
      operationId: debugBody
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Body'
      responses:
        204:
          description: "No Content"
components:
  schemas:
    Body:
      type: object
      properties:
        something1:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        something2:
          type: string
      required:
        - something1
        - something2
